Features already implemented

  • Timeline

    The classic view in a DAW who allow users to place his clip in the different tracks, duplicate it, move it, delete it, etc...

  • Graph

    Our new vision of the music creation with module who allow users to add an effect on his clip more easily.

  • Module library

    A library of free module create by our team to allow users to start creating in Nema Studio.

  • Intuitivity

    A new way to make music much easier.

Next features

  • Collaboration

    Like all application today the collaboration in real time was a mandatory feature for Nema Studio.

  • Marketplace

    A place where all our community can create plugins or effect and propose them to members.

  • Module library

    More module going to be add with the time.
